Cell["\<\
This shows that for all 0<p\[LessEqual]1, the partial transposition has a \
negative eigenvalue. Therefore, the state must be entangled.\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->107484504,ExpressionUUID->"ac07a105-e20b-45d9-bc7e-c20075e356f1"],

