Cell["\<\
Let us first examine a single pair of partially entangled qubits.  First, \
construct a superposition of the two computational basis states with \
different amplitudes.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->963914888,ExpressionUUID->"cad4f3a3-140a-4db2-a90b-5ae771db46e1"],

