Cell["\<\
Note that even through the state exhibits a maximal entanglement between the \
control and target registers, it is product state between two registers \
respectively containing qubits 1 and 3 and qubits 2 and 4.\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->1857015655,ExpressionUUID->"74be61a0-1f15-4a7c-bb65-ce2fd0a05109"],

